  "description": "<div id=\"product-detail\">\n\n    <h4>Application:</h4>\n    <ul>\n        <li>1988-1999 Chevy/GMC trucks and SUVs (2WD &amp; 4WD) with 5.0L / 5.7L (305/350 cu. in.)</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h4>Features:</h4>\n    <ul>\n        <li>Excellent quality and durability to improve vehicle performance</li>\n        <li>Fully mandrel bent tubes made of high quality 16-gauge mild steel</li>\n        <li>Head flanges laser-cut from high quality 5/16-inch thick steel plates</li>\n        <li>Flange flattened by a hydraulic press for precise and leak-free sealing</li>\n        <li>All joints are TIG welded to prevent cracking and wear</li>\n        <li>Black paint coating, can withstand up to 500 ¡æ</li>\n        <li>Accessories in the photos are included</li>\n        <li>1 year warranty for any manufacturing defect</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h4>Technical Specifications:</h4>\n    <ul>\n        <li>Header Type: Long Tube / Full Length</li>\n        <li>Primary Diameter: 1-5/8 in. (42mm)</li>\n        <li>Collector Diameter: 2-1/2 in. (64mm)</li>\n        <li>Head Flange Thickness: 5/16 in. (8.0mm)</li>\n        <li>Pipe Thickness: 16 gauge (1.5mm)</li>\n        <li>Material: Mild Steel</li>\n        <li>Finish: Black Paint</li>\n    </ul>\n\n</div>\n",
